      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SON OF ZATARA (3) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for four wins and five minors. Scored by 2 lengths last time (17.18) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. CATHY'S GIRL (1) collided with another runner and finished a well held 6 lengths eighth (17.54) last time in a Grade 4 at this track over 300m. Worth following up. PROPULSIVE (2) was below best at his last start when 7th at this track following a win (17.18) there two back. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Has won three of three starts from this draw. One of the better chances. ERAMOSA (6) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
